overview: Mia get's the role of a lifetime, but falling in love wasn't part of her contract. Leo their Manager must do all he can to keep the girls safe from their unstable landlord who is on the edge mentally. Will he win over her love and affection, or will he have to take drastic measures to keep her in his life. Mia might have danced into the wrong house but everything happens for a reason.
title: Mia
